br />\n要點釋法先可以演繹到冇抵觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點釋都得架喇<br />\nby the way 呢個時候仲講基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最終解釋權及修改權在人大"},{"pid":"d2cf57a4c03ce454169efd194e3652978591da92","tid":497488,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T23:07:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>「第七十五條<br />\n香港特別行政區立法會舉行會議的法定人數為不少於全體議員的二分之一。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議事規則由立法會自行制定，但不得與本法相抵觸。」<br />\n<br />\n要點釋法先可以演繹到冇抵觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點釋都得架喇<br />\nby the way 呢個時候仲講基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英文版（雖然係以中文為準，但參考下）<br />\n&quot; Article 75. The quorum for the meeting of the Legislative Council of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region shall be not less than one half of all its members. The rules of procedure of the Legislative Council shall be made by the Council on its own, provided that they do not contravene this Law.&quot;</blockquote><br />\n全體委員會(Committee of the whole)只係一個包括所有立法會議員嘅委員會，而委員會法定人數基本法係冇指定。"},{"pid":"324e5404511bc6e8933a74b89da9b47014268b54","tid":497488,"uid":1441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T23:31:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「第七十五條<br />\n香港特別行政區立法會舉行會議的法定人數為不少於全體議員的二分之一。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議事規則由立法會自行制定，但不得與本法相抵觸。」<br />\n<br />\n要點釋法先可以演繹到冇抵觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到時話基本法打錯字咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffdd5efb88dff979de425e4c7b81127a45016154","tid":497488,"uid":47674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T23:32:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>「第七十五條<br />\n香港特別行政區立法會舉行會議的法定人數為不少於全體議員的二分之一。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議事規則由立法會自行制定，但不得與本法相抵觸。」<br />\n<br />\n要點釋法先可以演繹到冇抵觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoj